Waqti ka dib, gargaarka Shiinaha ayaa sidoo kale la aqbalay meelo kale oo Latin America iyo Afrika ah. 2da Abriil, Hay'adda Amniga Adduunka ayaa bilaabay hawlgallo gargaarka degdegga ah ee dalalka soo koraya.
WHO waxay ku talineysaa tallaabooyinka ay dowladda Shiinaha ku qaadatay xakamaynta iyo xakamaynta cudurka.
WHO waxay kala saartey cudurka SARS ee 2002-2004, oo ay dowladda Shiinaha ku eedeysay inay si xun u sababtay iyo inay ku adkeysatay tallaabooyinka ka hortagga iyo xakamaynta, iyo cudurkaas oo ay dowladda dhexe "ugu baaqday in ay soo bandhigto warbixin ku saabsan saddex qof oo la dilay ka hor xafladaha sanadka cusub".
Bishii Janaayo 23, iyadoo laga jawaabayo cabashooyinka dowladda dhexe ee ku aaddan in ay hoos u dhigto khatarta ka jirta nidaamka tallaalka ee Wuhan, wakiilka WHO Gauden Galea wuxuu ogaaday in "aan jirin wax saameyn ah oo WHO ay sameysay", taas oo ah "tallaabo muhiim ah oo lagu xakameynayo cudurka heerka ugu sarreeya" wuxuuna ugu yeeray "mid aan horay loo arag taariikhda caafimaadka".Bishii Janaayo 30, ka dib markii la ogaaday in laga helay gudbinta bini'aadamka ee bini'aadamka ee ka baxsan Shiinaha iyo kororka heerarka cudurka ee dalalka kale, WHO waxay ku dhawaaqday cudurka inay tahay Cudurka Caafimaadka Adduunka ee Caafimaadka (PICHE), taas oo ah tallaalka ugu horreeya ee PICHE ee nidaamka degdegga ah ee laga soo bilaabo cudurka 2009.
Agaasimaha guud ee WHO Tedros Adhanom ayaa sheegay in PHEIC ay sabab u tahay "in ay ku faafto adduunka oo dhan, gaar ahaan dalalka leh heerar hoose oo dhimashada iyo nidaamyada caafimaadka ee aan laheyn.
Iyada oo laga jawaabayo hoos u dhaca safarka, Tedros wuxuu sheegay in "aan la joojin karin xeerarka ka hortagaya safarka caalamiga ah iyo ganacsiga" iyo in "WHO ay ku talineyso in la yareeyo ganacsiga ama ka hortagga".
Bishii Febraayo 5, WHO waxay ugu baaqday bulshada caalamka inay qorsheeyaan $675 milyan oo gargaar ah oo loogu talagalay dalalka dhaqaalaha hooseeya, iyadoo si degdeg ah ugu baaqeysa in la siiyo gargaar dalalka "aan haysan wax nidaam ah oo ay ku xakameeyaan cudurrada, xitaa haddii ay soo baxaan".
Tedros wuxuu intaas ku daray in "anu nahay kuwo xoog badan sida xubnaha ugu daciifsan" wuxuuna ugu baaqay bulshada caalamiga ah inay "ka hortagaan hadda ama ay sii kordhiyaan mustaqbalka". 11-kii Febraayo, WHO waxay shir jaraa'id ku soo bandhigtay COVID-19 magaca cudurka.
Maalintan, Tedros wuxuu sheegay in Xoghayaha Guud ee Qaramada Midoobay António Guterres uu ku qasbanaaday inuu siiyo "wax kasta oo siyaasadeed ee Qaramada Midoobay ee jawaabta".
Hay'adaha kale ee UN Disease Control ayaa ka shaqeynaya jawaabta, taas oo ka dhigan jawaabta guud ee Qaramada Midoobay, taas oo WHO ay sheegtay inay mas'uul ka tahay "jawaab degdeg ah oo caafimaad oo ay hay'adaha kale ku siin karaan khibradooda si ay uga shaqeeyaan arrimaha cudurka bulshada oo dhan, iyo dhammaan qaybaha bulshada".
Bishii Febraayo 14, Kooxda Shaqada ee Shiinaha ayaa la aasaasay si ay u soo dirto wakiilo caalami ah oo WHO ah oo ku sugan Shiinaha si ay uga caawiyaan xakamaynta iyo baaritaanka "caawinta iyo faafinta cudurka" ee dalka iyada oo la kaashanayo xiriirada la leh machadyada cilmi baarista ee qiimaha leh iyo dibedda si ay ula tacaalaan "hawlaha ka socda gobollada iyo gobollada, magaalooyinka iyo tuulooyinka".Bishii Febraayo 25, WHO waxay sheegtay in "dunidu ay u baahan tahay inay sameyso qorshe diyaarinta cudurka faafa ee coronavirus", waxayna sidoo kale sheegtay in marka ay dhacdo in ay jirto wax ka qabashada cudurka, dalalka iyo adduunka oo dhan ay ku jiraan "qorshe diyaarinta".
Iyada oo laga jawaabayo cudurka ka dilaacay Iran, WHO waxay u dirtay Kooxda Shaqada ee la xiriirta si ay u falanqeeyaan xaaladda.Bishii Febraayo 28, mas'uuliyiinta WHO waxay sheegeen in baaritaanka caalamiga ah ee cudurka coronavirus uu ka bilaaban doono "si toos ah" ilaa "si toos ah", taas oo ah heerka ugu dambeeya ee muhiimka ah ee baaritaanka xaaladda cudurka.
Mike Ryan, oo ah maamulaha barnaamijyada degdegga ah ee caafimaadka ee WHO, ayaa warbaahinta u sheegay in "Tani ay u egtahay in ay tahay tijaabo dhab ah oo ay dawladaha adduunka oo dhami ku sameeyaan: Aan is-weydiino.
Fayrasku wuxuu noqon karaa mid aan la xalin karin waana in la diyaariyaa", iyadoo la samaynayo tallaabooyin jawaab celin ah oo ka dhigi kara adduunka mid ka mid ah "kuwa ugu xun ee jira".
Ryan ayaa intaas ku daray in xogta hadda jirta ay siin doonto mas'uuliyiinta caafimaadka ee caalamiga ah, isagoo sheegay in warbixinta ay muujineyso "in aan aaminsanahay in qof kasta oo adduunka ah uu la kulmi doono fayraska".
Bishii Maarso, WHO ayaa ku dhawaaqday coronavirus inuu yahay cudur faafa.
Agaasimaha Guud ayaa sheegay in WHO ay "si xoog leh uga walwalsan tahay cudurrada faafa iyo faafitaanka, iyo sidoo kale cudurrada qarsoon". WHO waxay la xiriiri kartaa macluumaad muhiim ah oo ku saabsan waxa loo baahan yahay si loo xakameeyo cudurka caalamiga ah, iyo ugu dambeyntii warbixinta sida xaaladaha caafimaadka dadweynaha iyo ku darista fayraska cudurrada caalamiga ah.
Tirada ayaa sidoo kale ku xiran warqad uu u diray madaxa WHO Tedros Adhanom oo uu ku dhawaaqay inuu iska casilay, oo ay saxiixeen 733,000 oo qof 6dii Abriil.
26 Maarso 2020, khabiirada caafimaadka ee Qaramada Midoobay ayaa sameeyay 10kii baaritaan ee ugu horreeyay ee lagu xakameynayo cudurrada faafa ee COVID-19 ee adduunka.
Kooxda aqoonyahanada ayaa sheegtay in qof kasta oo lagu eedeeyay inuu ku qasbay inuu qof ku dhaawaco, dowladdu ay leedahay masuuliyad.
Kooxdu waxay soo saartay in nidaamyada aan lahayn ama aan lahayn daryeel caafimaad aysan noqon karin hab lagu qiimeeyo dadka kale.
Xildhibaanada ayaa sidoo kale xusay in qof walba uu xaq u leeyahay daryeel caafimaad, oo ay ku jiraan dadka qaba cudurrada dhalashada, dadka ka tirsan kooxaha ay ka yar yihiin, dadka waayeelka ah, dadka ku beddelay qaab nololeedkooda, dadka hoy la'aanta ah, dadka ku nool deegaano aad u adag, dadka xabsiga ku jira, iyo dadka qaba cudurrada difaaca iyo kooxaha kale ee u baahan caawimaadda dowladda.
Hay'adaha dowladda ee adduunka ayaa ku dhibtoonaya inay wax ka qabtaan dhibaatooyinka dhaqaale iyo amniga bulshada ee ay keentay cudurka COVID-19.
Ururka Isbahaysiga Horumarinta Amniga ayaa soo bandhigay dadaal ay ku siinayaan warbixinno waqtigeeda ku habboon oo ku saabsan siyaasadda adduunka oo dhan, iyo fikradaha iyo khilaafaadka.
Laga soo bilaabo siyaasadaha lagu xoojinayo nidaamyada caafimaadka iyo badbaadada adduunka ilaa ka hortagga dhibaatada joogitaanka iyo yareynta safarka, xarunta hawlaha waxaa ka mid ah Qorshaha Siyaasadda Qaranka, oo doonaya inay ka caawiso waddamada inay dibadda wax ku bartaan oo ay ku dadaalaan ka hortagga jawaabta caalamiga ah ee cudurka faafa ee coronavirus.
Dowladda Shiinaha ayaa waxaa ku bogaadiyay Mareykanka, Madaxa Xafiiska Golaha Wasiirada ee UK Michael Gove, iyo Madaxweynaha Brazil Jair Bolsonaro iyo Eduardo Bolsonaro si ay ula tacaalaan cudurka faafa, oo ka bilaabmay gobolka Hubei, ee Shiinaha.
Maamulada gobollada kale ee Xisbiga Shuuciga ee Shiinaha (CPC) ayaa la weydiiyay inay ka hortagaan in la xakameeyo dadka ku nool bartamaha Shiinaha, oo ah calaamad muujinaysa in ay tahay jawaab siyaasadeed oo ku saabsan cudurka gobolka.
Warbaahinta qaar waxay u maleynayaan in tallaabadaasi ay faa'iido u leedahay ilaalinta xoghayaha koowaad ee Xisbiga Shuuciga ee Shiinaha Xi Jinping ee ka hortagga cabsida dadweynaha ee cudurka coronavirus.
Qaar ka mid ah saraakiisha Shiinaha, sida Zhao Lijan ayaa diiday aqoonsiga ugu horreeya ee ku saabsan cudurka coronavirus ee ka dhashay Wuhan, iyadoo la tixgelinayo wararka ku saabsan COVID-19 oo ka yimid Mareykanka ama Talyaaniga.
Maamulka Mareykanka Donald Trump ayaa ku tilmaamay coronavirus "Cudurka Shiinaha" ama "Cudurka Wuhan" wuxuuna sheegay in Shiinaha uu "soo bandhigay fayras kale oo hadda ah cudur faafa", taas oo ay sidoo kale falanqeeyayaashu ku eedeeyeen inay tahay khiyaano iyo "xumaan ku ah mas'uuliyiinta dowladda ee xakameynta cudurka".
Wargeyska Daily Beast ayaa helay warqad ka timid dowladda Mareykanka oo muujineysa warbixinta ay soo saartay Hay'adda Amniga Qaranka, oo lagu magacaabo "Wax walba waxay ku saabsan yihiin Shiinaha.
Waxaa la noo sheegay in ay tahay in la isku dayo in wararka loo gudbiyo qaab kale, oo ay ku jiraan warbaahinta iyo warbaahinta".Warbaahinta sida Politico, Foreign Policy, iyo Bloomberg ayaa tilmaamay in dhammaan siyaabaha ay Shiinaha ugu caawineyso ay yihiin mid caalami ah oo lagu muujiyo.
