Xakamaynta khatarta shaqada ee COVID-19
Xakamaynta halista shaqada ee COVID-19 waa habka loo adeegsado caafimaadka iyo caafimaadka goobta shaqada si looga hortago cudurka faafa ee coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19).
Xakamaynta khatarta goobta shaqada waxay ku kala duwan tahay goobta shaqada iyo nooca shaqada, iyadoo lagu saleynayo qiimeynta halista joogitaanka, heerarka cudurka bulshada, iyo waxyaabaha ka hortagaya shaqaalaha laga yaabo inay ku dhacaan COVID-19.
Maamulka Badbaadada iyo Caafimaadka ee Mareykanka (OSHA) ayaa sheegay in hawlaha yaryar aysan wax khatar ah u keenin in ay yareeyaan isdhexgalka dadweynaha ama shaqaalaha kale, taas oo ay ugu horeyn ku talinayso tallaabooyinka ka hortagga cudurka, sida gacmaha dhaqidda, shaqaalaha yar ee guriga jooga marka ay jiran yihiin, ilaalinta neefsashada, iyo nadiifinta iyo nadiifinta dharka shaqada.
Shaqooyinka halista ah waxaa ka mid ah dadka ku nool ama ku nool meelaha aan la aqoonsan ama aan la aqoonsan COVID-19, laakiin laga yaabo inay ku dhacaan cudurka iyada oo loo marayo faafitaanka bulshada ee hadda jira ama safarada caalamiga ah.
Waxay ka kooban tahay shaqaalaha leh xirfado badan oo bulsho sida dugsiyada, goobaha shaqada ee dadku ku badan yihiin, meelaha ay ku badan yihiin dukaamada.
Xakamaynta khatarta kooxdan, marka lagu daro tallaabooyinka ka hortagga cudurka ee aasaasiga ah, waxaa ka mid ah in la ilaaliyo amarrada ka hortagga cudurka faafa, dharka daboolaya qallalka, iyo dharka ilaalinta shaqsiyeed ee la heli karo haddii aad la xiriirto qof qaba COVID-19.
OSHA waxay liis gareysaa shaqaalaha caafimaadka iyo shaqaalaha caafimaadka ee dhimashada sida qof la xaqiijiyay ama qof laga yaabo inuu qabo COVID-19 inay yihiin halis weyn, taas oo kordhinaysa halista weyn ee shaqaalaha ay ku jiraan marka ay sameeyaan tallaabooyin aerosol ah, ama ay qaataan, ama ay la macaamilaan daawooyinka, qof qaba ama laga yaabo inuu qabo COVID-19.
Xakamaynta khatarta ee muhiimka u ah shaqaalaha noocan ah waxaa ka mid ah ilaalada injineernimada sida hawada qolka, iyo qalabka daboolka ee la xiriira shaqada.
Cudurka COVID-19 wuxuu yeelan karaa khatar badan oo ku saabsan goobta shaqada.
Shaqaalaha ayaa laga yaabaa inay ka maqnaadaan shaqada sababtoo ah cudur, daryeel, ama cabsi ka qabashada cudurka.
Sharaxaadaha ganacsiga way kala duwanaan karaan, labadaba marka loo eego alaabta la iibsado, iyo habka loo helo alaabtaas (sida iibinta marka ay wax badan ka sii daran yihiin, ama kuwa guriga ku soo dira ama kuwa baabuurta ku iibiya).
Ugu dambeyntii, soo dejinta alaabada ka imanaya meelaha ay saameyn weyn ku yeelatay COVID-19 ayaa la joojin karaa. Qorshe ama jawaab-celin cudurku ku yimaado ayaa laga yaabaa inay faa'iido u leedahay ilaalinta howlaha.
Qorshahani waxay yareeyaan khataraha la xiriira dhammaan goobaha shaqada iyo hawlaha la midka ah, sida is-xidhka, waxyaabaha khatarta u ah guriga iyo bulshada, iyo waxyaabaha khatarta u ah dadka kale ee ka shaqeeya sida qiiqa ama cudurrada soo socda.
