Waxay ku saleysan tahay cilmi baaris ku saabsan buugga bilaashka ah ee "Apps Gone Rogue: Maintaining Personal Privacy in an Epidemic" oo la daabacay bishii Maarso 2020. Nidaamkan oo kale ayaa ah nidaamka SafeTrace ee ay samaysay Enigma MPC, koox kale oo ka shaqeysa horumarinta nidaamyada aqoonsiga oo sidoo kale laga helay MIT Media Lab.
