Magacyada rasmiga ah ee COVID-19 iyo SARS-CoV-2 ayaa la daabacay 11 Febraayo 2020.
Sababtoo ah xaddidaadaha ku jira iibka alaabta, soo saarayaasha alaabtu waxay soo saaraan alaabada caafimaadka sida qalabka lagu nadiifiyo iyo qalabka neefsashada.
Hal tijaabo, markii isbitaal ku yaal Talyaaniga uu si deg deg ah u dalbaday qalab hawada lagu buufiyo, macaamilku ma uusan soo bandhigin waqtiga la dalbaday, macaamil kale oo aan la aqoon ayaa ka baaray qalabka oo soo saaray 100 habeenkii.
Ka dib markii uu dillaacay COVID-19, wararka, wararka soo socda ama warbixinnada la wadaago waxay ku tiirsan yihiin caalamiga ah ee la xiriira soo-gaadhista, socodka, ka hortagga, daaweynta iyo calaamadaha cudurka.
Dadka ayaa u muuqda inay u badan tahay inay fayras ku faafi karaan xayawaanka kale.
Daraasaddan ayaa lagu ogaan doonaa saameynta ay leedahay fayraska ku jira digirta, shimbirrada, iyo shimbirrada.
Ma jiro daawo ama tallaal waxtar leh oo lagu daaweyn karo cudurka.
Cilmi-baarista caalamiga ah ee tallaalka iyo daaweynta COVID-19 ayaa ku dadaalaya in ay soo saaraan kooxo, kooxo caafimaad iyo cilmi-baarayaal.
Bishii Maarso, Hay'adda Caafimaadka Adduunka ayaa bilowday "Tijaabooyinka SOlidarity" si loo qiimeeyo khatarta daaweynta ee afar daaweyn oo isku dhafan oo muujinaya faa'iidooyin badan.
Ma jiro tallaal la heli karo, laakiin kooxo badan ayaa ka shaqeynaya tijaabooyinka tallaalka ee xoogga leh.
Waxqabadyada tallaalka ee SARS-Cov waxay muhiim u yihiin SARS-CoV iyo SARS-CoV-2 labadaba waxay u shaqeeyaan ACE2 si ay u galaan jirka aadanaha.
Waxaa jira talaalooyin badan oo la baaro.
Ugu horreyn, cilmi baarayaashu waxay rabaan inay soo saaraan tallaal ka hortag ah fayraska.
Isticmaalka fayraska noocaas ah, haddii uu shaqeynayo ama dhinto, waxay u baahan tahay in la abuuro jawaab difaaca jirka ee cudurka COVID-19 ee cusub.
Habka labaad, kooxda tallaalka, waxay doonaysaa in ay soo saarto tallaal difaaca jirka u diidaya noocyada kale ee fayraska.
Sida SARS-CoV-2, noocyada kala duwan ee baaritaanka waxay ku lug leeyihiin borotiinka S-spike ee ka caawiya fayraska inuu galo hiddaha ACE2-ka.
Habka saddexaad waa tallaalka nucleic acid (DNA ama RNA, habka cusub ee lagu soo bandhigo tallaalka).
Tijaabooyinka tijaabada ah ee mid ka mid ah hababka ayaa loo baahan yahay in la tixgeliyo badbaadada iyo faa'iidada. 16-kii Maarso 2020, tijaabooyinka ugu horreeya ee tallaalka ayaa bilaabmay afar tijaabo oo leh afar qof.
Batalitu waxay leedahay xayawaanka aan khatar ahayn ee ku jira fayraska keena fayraska.Difaaca jirka ayaa lagu talinayaa inuu yahay tallaal lagu daaweyn karo SARS-CoV-2, laakiin cilmi baarayaasha qaar ayaa diidan.
Waxaa jiray in ka badan 300 tijaabooyin caafimaad oo cilmi baaris ah oo la sameeyay ilaa Abriil 2020.
Lix iyo laba tijaabo ayaa ka hadlaya daawooyinka lagu daro daaweynta dhirta, iyo afar daraasadood oo ku saabsan hydroxychloroquine ama chloroquine.
Daawada loo yaqaan 'anti-viral vaccine' ayaa ah nooca ugu badan ee baaritaanka lagu sameeyo Shiinaha, iyadoo tijaabooyinka wajiga III ee remdesivir ay ku jiraan dalal badan oo la filayo inay bilaabaan dhamaadka Abriil.
Tijaabooyinka isticmaalka tallaalka iyo daawooyinka COVID-19 ee soo socda ayaa bilaabmay inay muuqdaan, laga bilaabo Abriil 2020.
Waxaa la filayaa in tijaabo lagu sameeyo isticmaalka remdesivir, bisha Maarso 2020.
Waxqabadka tijaabada caafimaad waxaa lagu ogaaday bukaanada si taxadar leh u qaata remdesivir.
Tijaabooyinka heerka III ee bukaan-socodka ee ka socda Mareykanka, Shiinaha iyo Talyaaniga.Chloroquine, oo horey loogu isticmaali jiray daaweynta duumada, ayaa laga tijaabiyay Shiinaha bishii Febraayo 2020, iyadoo la helay natiijooyin hore.
Si kastaba ha ahaatee, waxaa jira khilaafaadyo la xiriira baaritaanka.
Maamulka caafimaadka ee Kuuriya iyo Shiinaha ayaa ku talinaya in la isticmaalo chloroquine.
Si kastaba ha noqotee, Machadka Wuhan ee Fayraska, oo ka warramaya in qiyaasta daawada ay tahay hal garaam maalintii, ayaa ka walaacsan in qiyaasta ay tahay mid aad u khatar badan oo dhimasho ah.
Bishii Maarso 28, 2020, FDA waxay soo saartay amar degdeg ah oo ku saabsan isticmaalka hydroxychloroquine iyo chloroquine iyada oo aan la oggolaanin dhakhaatiirta daryeela daaweynta dadka qaba COVID-19. Warqad muujinaysa 7 waxay tixgelineysaa interferon, ribavirin ama umifenovir si loo daaweeyo COVID-19.
Warbixinnada hore waxay muujinayaan in qiyaasta ribavirin ay waxtar u leedahay ka hortagga SARS-CoV-2 in vitro.
Nitazoxanide waxaa lagu talinayaa in lagu sameeyo daraasado in vivo ah ka dib markii heerarka heerkulka SARS-CoV-2 ay hoos u dhacaan. Daraasadaha ayaa muujinaya in helitaanka ugu horeeya ee borotiinka kor u kaca ee loo yaqaan 'transmembrane protease serine 2' (TMPRSS2) uu muhiim u yahay SARS-CoV-2 iyada oo la falgalaya qaataha ACE2.
Daraasadaha lagu sameeyay chloroquine iyo hydroxychloroquine oo leh ama aan lahayn azithromycin ayaa leh khilaafaadyo badan oo ka hortagaya in bulshadeena caafimaadku ay aqbalaan iyada oo aan la helin daraasado kale.Oseltamivir ma yareeyo SARS-CoV-2 in vitro iyo doorkeeda la ogyahay ee daaweynta COVID-19.
Xadgudubka cytokine wuxuu noqon karaa mid halis ah oo ka dhaca heerarka kale ee COVID-19 ee daran.
Waxaa jira caddayn ah in hydroxychloroquine ay leedahay awood ay ku xakameyso da'da cytokine. Tocilizumab waxaa loo geliyey nidaamka daaweynta ee Guddiga Caafimaadka Qaranka ee Shiinaha ka dib markii la dhammeeyo daraasad kale oo yar.
Waxaa lagu oggol yahay heerka 2 ee baaritaanka aan kala sooc lahayn ee Talyaaniga oo ah in aan la helin calaamadaha iyo baaritaanka cudurka dadka qaba cudurrada faafa.
Waxaa lagu daray baaritaanka heerka dhiigga ee loo yaqaan 'ferritin blood test' si loo ogaado hoos u dhaca cytokine, hawshu waxay tahay in la joojiyo dhacdooyinkaas, kuwaas oo u badan in ay u dhintaan dadka qaba cudurka.
Xakamaynta interleukin-6 ee soo-dhoweynta ayaa la ansixiyay FDA iyadoo lagu saleynayo daraasado lagu sameeyay daaweynta steroid-ka ee cytokine-ka ee ka soo baxa daaweynta CAR T-cell, 2017.
Xaaladdan oo kale, ama tijaabooyin la mid ah, ayaa si weyn u aqoonsan in tocilizumab uu muhiim u yahay daaweynta CRS.
Soo saarista difaaca jirka ee ka soo horjeeda cudurka COVID-19 ee loogu talagalay dadka u baahan ayaa lagu tijaabiyaa inay tahay habka difaaca ee aan la ogaan.
Nidaamkan waxaa loo isticmaalaa SARS laakiin waa mid waxtar leh.
Dilka fayraska waa habka ugu wanaagsan ee lagu daaweyn karo cudurka oo leh difaaca jirka ee aan la garan karin oo soo saari kara difaaca SARS-CoV-2.
Waxyaabaha kale, sida cytotoxity unugyada iyo/ama cunnada, ayaa laga yaabaa inay jiraan.
Nidaamyada daaweynta ee difaaca jirka ee caadiga ah, tusaale ahaan, difaaca jirka ee hal-cagaha leh, ayaa sii kordhaya.
Ka bixitaanka dhiigga qofka la daweeyay, oo ah dareeraha dhiigga ee laga soo qaatay bukaanada la daweeyey oo aan lahayn fayras, ayaa laga yaabaa inay kordhiso jawaabta cudurka.
Cudurka coronavirus, oo ah calaamado isku dhafan
Li Wenliang, oo ah dhakhtar ka tirsan Isbitaalka Dhexe ee Wuhan, ayaa helay COVID-19 wuxuuna dhintay ka dib markii uu ka hadlayay faafitaanka fayraska.
